**Topic: Integration by Parts**

Jude - 4th Jude #

f(uv)' = u(x)v'(x) + u'(x)v(x)

∫[f(uv)' dx] = ∫[u(x)v'(x) + u'(x)v(x)]

⟹ d/dx[uv] = uv' + u'v

So uv = ∫uv' dx + ∫u'v dx

# Sub in du = u' dx ⟹ also true

dv = v' dx
dv = v' dx

∴ uv = ∫u dv + ∫v du

[Boxed formula]: ∫u dv = uv - ∫v du
